Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.68,0:00:51.26,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年少女结成圆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.26,0:00:54.75,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸出的手划过又落下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.14,0:00:57.98,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法交错的幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:01.98,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旋转木马在空中旋转
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.00,0:01:05.49,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗的帷幕徐徐落下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.90,0:01:09.11,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密揭晓的神圣之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.75,0:01:14.68,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深夜开窗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:20.01,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召唤秘密的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:25.43,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掀起深红的窗帘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.77,0:01:29.45,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐去微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.49,0:01:33.83,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年啊 回归自我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.95,0:01:36.52,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘上特快列车
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.57,0:01:39.10,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带我去梦幻之岛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.10,0:01:44.46,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺取一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.60,0:01:47.36,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使被指指点点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.36,0:01:50.68,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以立刻逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.76,0:01:56.29,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一切中意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.49,0:02:03.30,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年少女结成圆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.30,0:02:06.73,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸出的手划过又落下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.17,0:02:09.98,Penguin_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮回的命运
